Package tourGuide.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GpsService
    GpsService interfaces with GpsUtil to perform associated tasks for main TourGuide application
    RewardsService
    RewardsService interfaces with RewardCentral and performs associated tasks for main TourGuide application
    TourGuideService
    TourGuideService performs operations for TourGuideController, as well as performing services for Tracker thread
    TripService
    TripService interfaces with TripPricer and performs associated tasks for main TourGuide application
    UserService
    UserService contains our collection of users, and performs associated tasks for main TourGuide application Currently, to allow concurrent access we use a ConcurrentMap to store Users.
